AB  - A multivariate framework is used in order to study the price formation of risky assets in the Spanish capital market. Issues regarding the efficiency of the Spanish value-weighted stock market index, the validity of equilibrium considerations, the size effect, and the nature of the return generating process during January are analyzed.
